
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-surajk-evpn-access-security-00.txt'>
    <title>"EVPN ACCESS SECURITY", Suraj Kumar, Deepak Kakrania, Vijay Duna</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-surajk-evpn-access-security-00.txt</link>
    <description>The draft defines a new BGP EVPN route message for syncing DHCP packet contents as well as snoop entry among PEs in an Ethernet Segment (ES).  The snoop entry is required to implement Dynamic ARP inspection (DAI), IP Source Guard (IPSG/IPSGv6) and IPv6 Neighbor Discovery Inspection (NDI) access security features.</description>
    <dc:date>2017-01-12T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
